{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 238.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember one time in the camps, he for Christmas vacation, I guess, Christmastime, he took off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he left food with a guy which used to work a coal mountain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other words, they were putting coals in one particular area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is the coal they were using at the factories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a guard usually guarding it-- guarding it-- I don't know why-- who would steal it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But anyway, and he would leave it with this guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This guy knew that he was giving me bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I didn't even know about it, but we worked so close to him that the guy came to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, you know, he's not here but he brought in some food for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so I figured, I've got to do something for the man once I came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But anyway, I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "During the first bombardment of that camp that I was there, they actually-- the Americans bombed the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some of the bombs fell in our camp also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But when the first-- they bombed the place for the first time, this man came to me, Kolojejchick, and he says to me, here is my clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Take my-- take my good clothes, because he was wearing the working clothes as a painter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He says, follow me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He says, I can hide you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this was in about August, September of 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when they bombed the-- the factory, all the Nazis, all the SS run away, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They-- a lot of the prisoners ran out of the factory because they didn't-- besides having guards with us at work, they also had surrounded the entire factory, which was fenced in, of course.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there were guards outside the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
